iaik.pdf.asn1objects

Class Spuri

  • java.lang.Object
    • iaik.pdf.asn1objects.SignaturePolicyQualifierInfo
      • iaik.pdf.asn1objects.Spuri
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    iaik.asn1.ASN1Type

    public class Spuri
extends SignaturePolicyQualifierInfo
    This class represents the signature policy qualifier of type spuri. The value of this signature policy qualifier is a IA5String, indicating the URI or URL reference to the signature policy.
